      <title>新兴货币下跌，墨西哥比索在美国就业数据公布后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/emerging-market-bonds-eye-payrolls-data-for-fresh-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国非农就业数据强于预期，市场对美联储再次大幅降息的预期降温，多数新兴市场货币延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/emerging-market-bonds-eye-payrolls-data-for-fresh-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 07:27:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美国股市因软着陆预期而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市上涨，因就业报告强于预期，凸显经济实力。该数据削弱了美联储下月再次大幅降息的预期，导致美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
